Project AI rules:

1. Always wrap file paths in quotes.
2. Never create folders with spaces.
3. Use PowerShell commands instead of cmd.
4. Prefer Copy-Item instead of copy.
5. Check if folders exist before writing files.
6. Keep project structure clean.

Folder structure:

/assets
/css
/js
/components

"Use only Windows PowerShell commands. Never use ls, rm, cat, touch. Use dir, del, type, New-Item instead."